data.name: MYKEY
data.description:
MYKEY (mykey.org) claims to be a self-sovereign identity system implemented on multiple public blockchains. The underlying protocol is called KEY ID. The focus on the project is claimed to be on social relationship and data protection. MYKEY aims to turn data ownership back to users, protecting user privacy from the ground up.
